io.prismic

Class Fragment.DocumentLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.prismic.WithFragments
      • io.prismic.Fragment.DocumentLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Fragment, Fragment.Link
    Enclosing interface:
    Fragment

    public static class Fragment.DocumentLink
extends WithFragments
implements Fragment.Link
    Link to a document within the same Prismic repository. It extends WithFragments, but for Prismic to return any fragment you need to use the fetchLink parameter when querying your repository.
